---
---

<section class="py-24 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-4">Dónde encontrarnos</h2>
      <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-dark leading-tight mb-6">Nuestra Ubicación</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Ven a visitarnos o ponte en contacto con nosotros. Estamos situados en una zona accesible de Madrid para brindarte la mejor atención.
      </p>
      <div class="w-20 h-1.5 bg-primary rounded-full mx-auto mt-8"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl shadow-dark/5 border border-white relative overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700"></div>
        
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden h-[500px] w-full bg-gray-100">
          <iframe 
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3037.2605342417!2d-3.5854884!3d40.4252117!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xd42301984252f85%3A0xc0f1717367808381!2sC.%20de%20Fuentelviejo%2C%2037%2C%20San%20Blas-Canillejas%2C%2028022%20Madrid!5e0!3m2!1ses!2ses!4v1710614141414!5m2!1ses!2ses" 
            width="100%" 
            height="100%" 
            style="border:0;" 
            allowfullscreen="" 
            loading="lazy" 
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
            title="Mapa de ubicación de ASISVE en Madrid"
            class="filter grayscale-[0.1] hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700"
          ></iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 p-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl text-primary">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-map-pin"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-dark">Dirección</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500">C. de Fuentelviejo, 37<br/>28022 Madrid, España</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl text-primary">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clock"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-dark">Horario</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500">Lunes - Viernes<br/>9:00 - 18:00</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="p-3 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl text-primary">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-external-link"><path d="M15 3h6v6"/><path d="M10 14 21 3"/><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-dark">Cómo llegar</h4>
              <a 
                href="https://www.google.com/maps/dir/?api=1&destination=C.+de+Fuentelviejo,+37,+San+Blas-Canillejas,+28022+Madrid" 
                target="_blank" 
                class="text-primary font-semibold hover:underline"
              >
                Ver en Google Maps
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
